2.1.	Processing of the User's personal data is provided for an action or a set of actions performed with personal data, including accumulation, storage, modification, addition, use, distribution, depersonalization, blocking and destruction of the User's personal data in accordance with the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan.
2.2.	The User's personal data is collected and processed by the KDIF for the following purposes:
2.2.1.	identification of the User registered in the mobile application, including by means of biometric identification or identification by mobile phone number by sending a one-time password to it;
2.2.2.	automation of the process of filling out an application by the User for an insurance refund;
2.2.3.	registration of the User to submit an application for an insurance refund through the User's personal account in the mobile application;
2.2.4.	providing an opportunity to view the amount of the insurance compensation to be paid, submitting an application for payment of the insurance compensation and using other services of the mobile application;
2.2.5.	receiving information about the status of the application for an insurance refund;
2.2.6.	storage and protection of personal data;
2.2.7.	making the payment of the insurance compensation and performing other tasks performed by the KFGD in accordance with the Law;
2.2.8.	the functioning of the mobile application.
3. Methods and terms of personal data processing
3.1.	 KDIF collects and processes the User's personal data through the mobile application, which is necessary to view the amount of the insurance compensation to be paid, and to receive an application from the User for an insurance refund, and also ensures the protection of the User's personal data.
3.2.	The methods of processing the User's personal data are non-automated and automated processing of the User's personal data.
3.3.	Automated processing of the User's personal data means processing of the User's personal data using computer technology.
3.4.	The non-automated processing of the User's personal data means the processing of the User's personal data without the use of computer technology.
3.5.	The User gives his consent to the collection and processing of his personal data for the storage period, which is determined by the date of achievement of the purposes of collection and processing, unless otherwise provided by the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan.
Rights and obligations of the KDIF
4.1.	KDIF has the right to:
4.1.1.	process the User's personal data using automation tools;
4.1.2.	stop processing and destroy the User's personal data in cases stipulated by the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan;
4.1.3.	require third parties to take legal, organizational and technical measures to ensure the protection, confidentiality, integrity and safety of the User's personal data;
4.1.4.	make changes and (or) additions to this Privacy Policy without the User's consent.
4.2	KDIF undertakes to:
4.2.1.	take the necessary legal, organizational and technical measures to ensure the protection, confidentiality, integrity and safety of the User's personal data from the moment of collection of such personal data until their destruction or depersonalization;
4.2.2.	comply with the User's rights in the field of personal data processing, as well as other requirements for the processing of personal data established by the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan.

5. Rights and obligations of the User

5.1.	The User, when processing his personal data in the mobile application, has the right to:
5.1.1.	have all the necessary rights that allow him to register and use the mobile application;
5.1.2.	use their personal data for any legitimate purposes, including for the purposes established by this Privacy Policy;
5.1.3.	withdraw their consent to the collection and processing of personal data in cases provided for by the Law of the Republic of Kazakhstan "On Personal Data and its Protection";
5.1.4.	change (update, supplement) their previously provided personal data in the mobile application.
5.2.	The User undertakes to:
5.2.1.	provide reliable information about themselves in the amounts necessary to use the mobile application;
5.2.2.	familiarize themlelves with the requirements of this Privacy Policy in a timely manner;
5.2.3.	correct the personal data processed in the mobile application in case of its inconsistency with the information available to the KDIF;
5.2.4.	independently monitor changes to this Privacy Policy by reviewing the current version posted on the Internet resource of the KDIF;
5.2.5.	perform other duties arising from the User during the processing of his personal data.
5.3.	The User is responsible in accordance with the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan for the accuracy of the information provided by the KDIF containing personal data.
6. Access to personal data and confidentiality
6.1.	The User's personal data may be transferred to a third party:
6.1.1.	with the User's consent to the processing of his personal data in cases that do not go beyond the purposes of their collection provided for in this Privacy Policy;
6.1.2.	if the transfer is provided for by the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan.
6.2.	KDIF, as well as third parties who gain access to the User's personal data, ensure their confidentiality by complying with the requirements to prevent their dissemination without the consent of the User or his legal representative or the presence of other legal grounds, if this is not related to the purposes specified in paragraph 2.2. of this Privacy Policy.
6.3.	Persons who have become aware of the User's personal data due to professional, official necessity, as well as labor relations, are obliged to ensure their confidentiality.
6.4.	Confidentiality of biometric data is established by the legislation of the Republic of Kazakhstan
